snippet.title: River City Ransom (NES) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A complete playthrough of Technos 1990 NES game, River City Ransom.


Man I love this game. It's essentially Final Fight with RPG trappings and SD characters, and it's done by Technos. What else do you want?
_______________
No cheats were used during the recording of this video. 

NintendoComplete (http://www.nintendocomplete.com/) punches you in the face with in-depth reviews, screenshot archives, and music from classic 8-bit NES games!
